  output.includes(`\n${CONFIG.completionSignal}`); // at end after newline

if (signalAtEnd || signalOnOwnLine) {
```

---

### Step 2: Add Module-Scope Process Reference
Add at line ~28 (after CONFIG):
```typescript
let currentProc: ReturnType<typeof Bun.spawn> | null = null;
```

### Step 3: Fix Output Replacement Logic
Replace lines 200-206 with:
