Wrap stream reading in try-finally:
```typescript
const reader = proc.stdout.getReader();
try {
  while (true) {
    const { done, value } = await reader.read();
    if (done) break;
    // ... processing ...
  }
} finally {
  reader.releaseLock();
}
```

