Replace line 291:
```typescript
// More specific error detection - look for actual error indicators
const hasErrors = exitCode !== 0 ||
  /(?:^|\n)\s*(?:Error:|ERROR:|Failed:|FAILED:)/m.test(output) ||
  output.includes('claude: error');
```

